dc_description_s:
This file provides Solano County, California General Plan Unincorporated Area Land Use information in ESRI polygon shapefile format.
Solano County General Plan Land Use and Circulation Layer as originally adopted by Board of Supervisor Resolution 81-180 on August 4, 1981 and last Amended by Board of Supervisor August 4, 2004.

dc_title_s: Solano County Unincorporated Areas Land Use
